title: SomeNews Radio - Not Really Much and Other Stuff
description: In the show today, not much really. But having said that this is one of the longest podcasts from a show that came out, so that "nothing" got stretched out a fair bit. Items included a few calls from people trying to help me come up with ideas, a story about a man who shoved snacks up his botty, Ed Sheran's Sing sounds a bit like MC Hammer and a lot of stuff about footballers eating.
